Transforms:
Tranform is nothing but transforming the existed element(such as circle, rectangular size box/div) into another/different shapes.

The transform CSS property lets you rotate, scale, skew, or translate an element.

Properties :
/* rotate: rotates the box clockwise/anti-clockwise to provided deg */
transform: rotate(360deg);
transform: rotate(-360deg);

/* scale increase/decreases the size of box */
transform: scale(2);
transform: scale(0.5);

/* skew: tilts the box */
transform: skew(45deg);
transform: skew(-45deg);

/* translate : moves the box into diff directions 
with respect to x and y axis */
transform: translate(500px);
transform: translate(-500px);
transform: translate(0px, 500px);
transform: translate(0px, -500px);
transform: translate(500px, 500px);
transform: translate(-500px, -500px)


